abstract: Iran's official Islamic Republic News Agency denies that American officials were ever in direct contact with the Iranian government over the alleged plot to assassinate Saudi Arabia's ambassador to the United States.
snippet: Iran’s official news agency insisted on Friday that American officials had not been in direct contact over the alleged plot to assassinate Saudi Arabia’s ambassador to the United States.
lead_paragraph: Iran’s official news agency insisted on Friday that American officials had not been in direct contact over the alleged plot to assassinate Saudi Arabia’s ambassador to the United States.
